---
---

<div>
  <div class="text-center mb-12">
    <span class="eyebrow">The path forward</span>
    <h2 class="mt-5 text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">
      What early students will say
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg copy-muted max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      These are the outcomes we're building toward. Help shape DEVS and become part of our founding cohort.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Expected Outcome 1 -->
    <div class="surface-card p-8">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-1 mb-4">
        <span class="text-[var(--color-accent-2)]">★</span>
        <span class="text-[var(--color-accent-2)]">★</span>
        <span class="text-[var(--color-accent-2)]">★</span>
        <span class="text-[var(--color-accent-2)]">★</span>
        <span class="text-[var(--color-accent-2)]">★</span>
      </div>
      
      <blockquote class="mb-6">
        <p class="text-base copy-muted italic">
          "I understand Git, code review, and sprint workflows—skills my bootcamp glossed over."
        </p>
      </blockquote>

      <div class="pt-4 border-t border-[var(--color-border)]">
        <p class="text-xs copy-subtle font-mono">Expected outcome: Git mastery</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Expected Outcome 2 -->
    <div class="surface-card p-8">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-1 mb-4">
        <span class="text-[var(--color-accent-2)]">★</span>
        <span class="text-[var(--color-accent-2)]">★</span>
        <span class="text-[var(--color-accent-2)]">★</span>
        <span class="text-[var(--color-accent-2)]">★</span>
        <span class="text-[var(--color-accent-2)]">★</span>
      </div>
      
      <blockquote class="mb-6">
        <p class="text-base copy-muted italic">
          "I have real projects to discuss in interviews, not just tutorials I followed."
        </p>
      </blockquote>

      <div class="pt-4 border-t border-[var(--color-border)]">
        <p class="text-xs copy-subtle font-mono">Expected outcome: Portfolio-ready work</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Expected Outcome 3 -->
    <div class="surface-card p-8">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-1 mb-4">
        <span class="text-[var(--color-accent-2)]">★</span>
        <span class="text-[var(--color-accent-2)]">★</span>
        <span class="text-[var(--color-accent-2)]">★</span>
        <span class="text-[var(--color-accent-2)]">★</span>
        <span class="text-[var(--color-accent-2)]">★</span>
      </div>
      
      <blockquote class="mb-6">
        <p class="text-base copy-muted italic">
          "I'm confident in standups, code reviews, and shipping features with a team."
        </p>
      </blockquote>

      <div class="pt-4 border-t border-[var(--color-border)]">
        <p class="text-xs copy-subtle font-mono">Expected outcome: Team-ready mindset</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Beta CTA -->
  <div class="mt-16 text-center">
    <div class="inline-block surface-card p-8 max-w-2xl border-2 border-[var(--color-accent-2)]/30">
      <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-4">
        Be a founding member
      </p>
      <p class="copy-muted mb-6">
        Join the beta cohort and help shape DEVS. You'll get early access, direct feedback opportunities, and lifetime credit.
      </p>
      <a href="#notify" class="btn-primary cta-glow inline-block">
        Join beta program <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
